        "content": "<p>Yes:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Int</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">dvd_gcd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">{</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">ℤ</span><span class=\"o\">}</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h2</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">k</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∣</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">↑</span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">i</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">gcd</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">j</span><span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>You can compose it with <code>Int.le_of_dvd {a b : ℤ} (bpos : 0 &lt; b) (H : a ∣ b) : a ≤ b</code> to get the function you need.</p>",
